3 1 E
3 2 W
1 1 1 2
3 2 E
3 2 W
1 1 1 4
3 2 W
2 1 3 \
3 2 W
3 2 E
3 1 S
</pre>
    </div>
    <table class="sample" summary="sample data">
      <tr>
        <th>Sample Input 1</th>
        <th>Sample Output 1</th>
